-- Reliance to Pay $1.35 Billion for Stake in Texas Shale Gas Field, FT Says
-- Jeran Wittenstein
-- 2010-06-21T21:39:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/reliance-to-pay-1-35-billion-for-stake-in-texas-shale-gas-field-ft-says.html

          
          
             Reliance Industries may announce as
early as tomorrow plans to buy a 45 percent stake in the Eagle
Ford shale gas field in south Texas for $1.35 billion, the
Financial Times reported, citing unidentified people familiar
with the situation.  
 The field is controlled by Pioneer Natural Resources, the
FT said.  
          
          


  


        